{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/unpredictable.png?t=1739269037\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Valor Of Man is a roguelike tactical RPG where enemies react to your actions. Lead your party of heroes as you anticipate and outsmart your enemies. Make careful decisions as you forge your path to victory.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Valor of Man Demo Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unique Reaction System &amp;\u00a0Emergent Tactical Combat</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/1-ezgif.com-resize__1_.gif?t=1739269037\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Roguelike Elements and Progression</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/2-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1739269037\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Procedurally Generated Map and Endless Replayability</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/3-ezgif.com-resize__1_.gif?t=1739269037\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Valor of Man Demo Content:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the Complete First Chapter (out of 3)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unleash the Power of 4 Hero Classes (out of 12) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover 120 Hero Abilities (out of 250)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gear Up with 85 Items (out of 250)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover 70 Powerful Artifacts (out of 150)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Best 3 Bosses, 6 Elites and 10+ Regular Foes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_pa